## Project Structure

```
src/main/java/<%= groupId.replace(/\./g, '/') %>/
├── config/              # Spring configuration (Security, JPA, OpenAPI)
├── controller/          # REST controllers (SampleController)
├── service/             # Business logic interfaces
│   └── impl/            # Service implementations (SampleServiceImpl)
├── repository/          # Data access — Spring Data JPA (SampleRepository)
├── domain/
│   └── entity/          # JPA entities (BaseEntity, SampleEntity)
├── dto/
│   ├── request/         # Inbound DTOs (SampleRequest)
│   └── response/        # Outbound DTOs (SampleResponse)
├── exception/           # Exception hierarchy + GlobalExceptionHandler
├── mapper/              # Entity ↔ DTO mappers (SampleMapper)
├── client/              # External service clients
├── util/                # Utilities (CorrelationIdFilter, MaskingUtil)
├── messaging/
│   ├── producer/        # Event producers (SampleEventProducer)
│   └── consumer/        # Event consumers (SampleEventConsumer)
└── specification/       # JPA Specifications for dynamic queries

src/main/resources/
├── application.yml              # Common configuration
├── application-local.yml        # Local dev profile
├── application-dev.yml          # Dev environment
├── application-sit.yml          # SIT environment
├── application-uat.yml          # UAT environment
├── application-prod.yml         # Production
├── db/migration/
│   └── V1__create_sample_table.sql  # Flyway migration
└── logback-spring.xml           # Logging (JSON in non-local)

src/test/java/<%= groupId.replace(/\./g, '/') %>/
├── config/              # TestContainersConfig (SQL Server)
├── controller/          # Controller slice tests (SampleControllerTest)
├── service/             # Unit tests (SampleServiceImplTest)
├── repository/          # Repository integration tests (SampleRepositoryTest)
├── integration/         # Full integration tests (SampleIntegrationTest)
└── fixture/             # Test data factory (TestDataFactory)
```

## Sample Vertical Slice

This project ships with a working **Sample** CRUD example that demonstrates all patterns end-to-end:

| Layer | File | Pattern |
|-------|------|---------|
| Entity | `SampleEntity` | JPA entity extending `BaseEntity`, audit fields, business methods |
| Repository | `SampleRepository` | Spring Data JPA + `JpaSpecificationExecutor` |
| Specification | `SampleSpecification` | Dynamic query composition with `.and()` / `.or()` |
| Service | `SampleServiceImpl` | `@Transactional`, Resilience4j, exception handling, logging |
| Controller | `SampleController` | REST API at `/api/v1/samples`, validation, pagination, proper HTTP status codes |
| DTOs | `SampleRequest` / `SampleResponse` | Java records with validation annotations |
| Mapper | `SampleMapper` | Static utility — entity ↔ DTO conversion |
<% if (messaging === 'Kafka') { %>| Messaging | `SampleEventProducer` / `SampleEventConsumer` | Kafka with manual ack, idempotent producer |
<% } else if (messaging === 'Azure Service Bus') { %>| Messaging | `SampleEventProducer` / `SampleEventConsumer` | Azure Service Bus (scaffolded, wire ServiceBusSenderClient) |
<% } %>| Tests | `SampleControllerTest` | `@WebMvcTest` — HTTP layer only, service mocked |
| Tests | `SampleServiceImplTest` | Mockito unit tests — business logic in isolation |
| Tests | `SampleRepositoryTest` | Integration test with real SQL Server (TestContainers) |
| Tests | `SampleIntegrationTest` | Full CRUD lifecycle — controller → service → repository |

> **Tip:** Use the Sample as a reference, then rename/replace with your domain entities.

## Key Decisions

- **Database:** SQL Server (Azure SQL in production)
- **Auth:** <%= authPattern %>
- **Messaging:** <%= messaging %>
- **Observability:** OpenTelemetry + Logstash JSON logging
- **Resilience:** Resilience4j (circuit breaker, retry, bulkhead)
